null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_49":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_49","name":"5ce9","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"These are the points which appears when the project is checked at first glance, however there are more missing points which could be done. However, the main aim was to give idea how to accomblish automated way of downloading youtube videos and releasing with Github actions.","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_50":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_50","name":"4109","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"I am personally using it for personal needs whenever I find useful playlist, I include it into playlist-list.csv file and pushing the changes by tagging the commit in semantic versioning format.","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[{"__typename":"Markup","type":"CODE","start":95,"end":112,"href":null,"anchorType":null,"userId":null,"linkMetadata":null}],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_51":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_51","name":"bf74","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"There are tons of other services which could be integrated such as Slack, Discord, Mail or any another notification systems and more, however, to keep the post short and do not bother you, it is enough for now as it is.","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_52":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_52","name":"3389","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"The rule for the workflow could be easily changed, like instead of running it in tagged commits, it can run in scheduled way by changing run condition only, as shown below.","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_53":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_53","name":"f685","type":"PRE","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"name: Download & Release Youtube Playlists","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_54":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_54","name":"1684","type":"PRE","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"on:\n  schedule:\n    - cron: '0 0 * * *' # every day at midnight ","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_55":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_55","name":"0397","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"If you require or would like to have more features, or fixes, suggestions and etc, you are more welcome to open issues.","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_56":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_56","name":"eec4","type":"H3","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"Github Limitations","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_57":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_57","name":"8a3e","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"Since we are using Github actions, we have some limitations regarding to usage of it.","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_58":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_58","name":"152b","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"The limitations regarding to file sizes in releases, according to Github Statement here: Distributing large binaries","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[{"__typename":"Markup","type":"A","start":89,"end":116,"href":"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.github.com\u002Fen\u002Ffree-pro-team@latest\u002Fgithub\u002Fmanaging-large-files\u002Fdistributing-large-binaries","anchorType":"LINK","userId":null,"linkMetadata":null}],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_59":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_59","name":"be7d","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"Basically, a file size which will be uploaded to releases should NOT exceeds 2 GB. However, keep in mind that it is per file, there is NO limitation for overall size of the release :). It means that repository will be updated to split files into chunks if size of the file exceeds 2 GB. So, in case of 15 GB of playlist, it should be uploaded in 2GB chunks to releases. (- a feature which is NOT exists on youtubeto yet -)","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[{"__typename":"Markup","type":"STRONG","start":65,"end":68,"href":null,"anchorType":null,"userId":null,"linkMetadata":null},{"__typename":"Markup","type":"STRONG","start":135,"end":137,"href":null,"anchorType":null,"userId":null,"linkMetadata":null},{"__typename":"Markup","type":"STRONG","start":406,"end":415,"href":null,"anchorType":null,"userId":null,"linkMetadata":null}],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_60":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_60","name":"2ae5","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"There are some more limitations:","hasDropCap":null,"dropCapImage":null,"markups":[],"codeBlockMetadata":null,"iframe":null,"mixtapeMetadata":null},"Paragraph:8d7b84ec45f2_61":{"__typename":"Paragraph","id":"8d7b84ec45f2_61","name":"f1ae","type":"P","href":null,"layout":null,"metadata":null,"text":"Job execution time — Each job in a workflow can run for up to 6 hours o